<% content_for :title, "Drink & Eat".html_safe %>

<div class="row">
  <div class="large-offset-4 large-8 columns">
    <h2>Our Coffee</h2>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="large-4 columns">
    <%= image_tag "latte_art.jpg", :class => "" %>
  </div>

  <div class="large-8 columns">
    <p>We take great pride in preparing our coffee and have the pleasure of working with specialist roasteries that purchase direct from the world's leading farms. Giving us a wide range of high quality and delicate profiles that are roasted to perfection.</p>

    <p>We are very proud to introduce <strong>"Exhibition"</strong>, our new signature house espresso. Roasted by the talented team at Nude Espresso who have been working very hard to create what can only be described as sweet nectar from the gods.</p>

    <p>Our first Exhibition blend is a harmonious combination of Brazilian and El Salvadorian produce, roasted to perfection. The espresso is rich and velvety with dark forest fruits of prunes and plums balanced by light lemon pie acidity. When paired with steamed milk the fruit notes take a back seat giving way to smooth toffee caramel.</p>

    <p>This coffee is so delicious it gives new meaning to the word caffeine addiction.</p>
  </div>
</div>

