  <div class="large-offset-4 large-8 columns">
    <h2>Our Tea</h2>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="large-4 columns">
    <%= image_tag "tea.jpg", :class => "" %>
  </div>

  <div class="large-8 columns">
    <p>Our teas are supplied by tea traders <a href="http://www.lalaniandco.com/">Lalani &amp; Co</a> who spend time every year visiting tea farms around the world to source only the highest quality teas. We brew our teas in homemade Gaiwans using exact recipes to ensure we get the best out of the leaves.</p>
  </div>
</div>

